\subtree{
\title{Conclusion}
\p{Stream-Chain enables sophisticated multi-step workflows by:}

\ul{
\li{\strong{Sequential Processing}: Each step builds on previous results}
\li{\strong{Context Preservation}: Full output history flows through chain}
\li{\strong{Flexible Orchestration}: Custom chains or predefined pipelines}
\li{\strong{Agent Coordination}: Natural multi-agent collaboration pattern}
\li{\strong{Data Transformation}: Complex processing through simple steps}
}

\p{Use \code{\startverb run\stopverb} for custom workflows and \code{\startverb pipeline\stopverb} for battle-tested solutions.}
}
}